195
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:16,278
Yes, sir.

196
00:12:25,328 --> 00:12:28,498
Mapo Bridge has suddenly...

197
00:12:28,498 --> 00:12:29,958
Ready?

198
00:12:30,667 --> 00:12:31,793
Hold on.

199
00:12:31,793 --> 00:12:33,879
