234
00:14:44,843 --> 00:14:47,762
Chief? I'm Producer JUNG
of Daily Topic.

235
00:14:47,762 --> 00:14:51,016
- You can't just come in and...
- Producer JUNG?

236
00:14:51,016 --> 00:14:56,354
