and why'.

251
00:15:43,526 --> 00:15:48,406
Then, he surrenders at the end.

252
00:15:48,406 --> 00:15:52,077
He wanted to commit suicide,
but changed after talking to me.

253
00:15:52,077 --> 00:15:58,208
