and in handcuffs at the end.

254
00:15:58,208 --> 00:15:59,250
- Can you do it?
- Yes.

255
00:15:59,250 --> 00:16:00,669
30 seconds left.

256
00:16:00,669 --> 00:16:03,797
Wait! This is ours.
What's the rush?

257
00:16:03,797 --> 00:16:06,091
Give me 5 minutes
to make a call.

258
00:16:06,091 --> 00:16:09,678
